  "description": "Dark matter is matter that interacts gravitationally but not electromagnetically -- invisible to all telescopes across the entire [electromagnetic spectrum](../../../terms/electromagnetic-spectrum.md), detectable only through its gravitational effects on visible matter and [light](../../../terms/light.md).",
